---
title: Coconut Chicken Adobo with Garlic Rice
description: Adobo is the national dish of the Philippines, and while there are likely as many variations on it as there are Philippine islands, one thing remains constant: the backbone of this dish is a sauce that's deeply savoury with a good splash of vinegary twang!
